				<wikidot:authorName>Judge_Dreddpool</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2984376</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">My&nbsp;thoughts&nbsp;on&nbsp;this&nbsp;entry&nbsp;(Collapsible&nbsp;for&nbsp;image)</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>I only just found this SCP through a DeviantArt post today &amp; I'll be honest, this is now one of my SCP's that I've read.</p> <p>Take my plus +1 Author. Seriously, take it.</p> Also, in regards to the snake:<br /> <img src="https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/001/306/202/dda.png" alt="dda.png" class="image" /></div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
