					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12498093#post-4357146</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12498093/scp-4265#post-4357146</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2019 16:52:59 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>peppermint_legos</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5515758</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>How does the snake know about SCP objects it hasn't seen? Does it also have limited omniscience?</p> <p>The first addendum didn't really do anything for my enjoyment, I feel like it could be discarded and reworked into the rest of the piece.</p> <p>The logs of films are interesting but not interesting enough to stand on their own: I wanted this story to go further down whatever weird rabbit hole you're envisioning!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
